(1247, 'options_our_gallery_settings_en_our_gallery_description', 'Become an owner of a hand-painted portrait and put the spirit into your photo. Here we have gathered all kinds of portraits of our professional artists so you can grab some inspiration and choose the best option for you. Our portraits are creative and special gifts that you can present to your loved ones and capture the timeless moments.', 'no'),
