(4090, 341, 'text', 'Thank you for choosing Painted Desire! A handmade portrait is the best gift you can make to impress your loved ones. Unique, special, creative - it’s all about Painted Desire portrait. To make your order procedure simpler, we created 3 easy steps to follow.'),
(4091, 341, '_text', 'field_5fb4b21607dea'),
(4092, 341, 'our_steps_0_title', 'Portrait Characteristic'),
(4093, 341, '_our_steps_0_title', 'field_5fb4b24007dec'),
(4094, 341, 'our_steps_0_text', 'To order the best portrait ever, first, you have to choose the subject - one person, a couple, a pet, landscape, etc. Decide what technique would you like our artist to use to create your portrait: charcoal or oil paints.\r\n\r\nAfter that, choose the preferred size and the background.'),
(4095, 341, '_our_steps_0_text', 'field_5fb4b25107ded'),
