(4129, 347, '_title', 'field_5fb4b1d307de9'),
(4130, 347, 'text', 'Thank you for choosing Painted Desire! A handmade portrait is the best gift you can make to impress your loved ones. Unique, special, creative - it’s all about Painted Desire portrait. To make your order procedure simpler, we created 3 easy steps to follow.'),
(4131, 347, '_text', 'field_5fb4b21607dea'),
(4132, 347, 'our_steps_0_title', 'Portrait Characteristic'),
(4133, 347, '_our_steps_0_title', 'field_5fb4b24007dec'),
(4134, 347, 'our_steps_0_text', 'To order the best portrait ever, first, you have to choose the subject - one person, a couple, a pet, landscape, etc. Decide what technique would you like our artist to use to create your portrait: charcoal or oil paints.\r\n\r\nAfter that, choose the preferred size and the background.'),
