(4509, 371, 'faq_0_items_0_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">To simplify the process of ordering, we created 3 simple steps that will help\r\nyou to become a happy owner of handmade portrait:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"faq__description-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ Choose the portrait characteristic (number of subjects, painting\r\ntechniques, size, etc.)</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ Upload a photo</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ Approve your order</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"faq__description\">To see more detailed instructions, go to the Procedure page.</p>'),
(4510, 371, '_faq_0_items_0_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4511, 371, 'faq_0_items_1_title', 'What medium do you use to create a portrait?'),
(4512, 371, '_faq_0_items_1_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4513, 371, 'faq_0_items_1_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">We have two kinds of portraits:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"faq__description-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ a charcoal portrait is painted on a high-quality thick paper with\r\nhighly intensive charcoal pencils;</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ an oil portrait is created on solid canvas with durable and intense\r\ncolors and doesn’t need any protective glass.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4514, 371, '_faq_0_items_1_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4515, 371, 'faq_0_items_2_title', 'What should I know to receive the portrait?'),
(4516, 371, '_faq_0_items_2_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4517, 371, 'faq_0_items_2_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">When you order a portrait, we give you a tracking code. It’s assigned to track\r\nyour package and then pick it up at the post office.</p>'),
(4518, 371, '_faq_0_items_2_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4519, 371, 'faq_0_items', '3'),
(4520, 371, '_faq_0_items', 'field_5fb4d0a982848'),
(4521, 371, 'faq_1_title', 'Editing photo'),
(4522, 371, '_faq_1_title', 'field_5fb4d0a482847'),
(4523, 371, 'faq_1_items_0_title', 'What quality should my photo be?'),
(4524, 371, '_faq_1_items_0_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4525, 371, 'faq_1_items_0_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">You can take a picture of your own photo. The quality doesn’t need to be the\r\nhighest - we have programs that make the photo more pixelated. If it’s too blurred, we will inform you</p>'),
(4526, 371, '_faq_1_items_0_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4527, 371, 'faq_1_items_1_title', 'Is it possible to create a portrait from individual photos?'),
(4528, 371, '_faq_1_items_1_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4529, 371, 'faq_1_items_1_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">Yes, we use professional programs like Photoshop to make the highest-quality\r\nportraits. Also, we give the preview of the portrait for you to imagine how it will look like.</p>'),
(4530, 371, '_faq_1_items_1_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4531, 371, 'faq_1_items', '2'),
(4532, 371, '_faq_1_items', 'field_5fb4d0a982848'),
(4533, 371, 'faq_2_title', 'Prices and Payments'),
(4534, 371, '_faq_2_title', 'field_5fb4d0a482847'),
(4535, 371, 'faq_2_items_0_title', 'How much does the portrait cost?'),
(4536, 371, '_faq_2_items_0_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4537, 371, 'faq_2_items_0_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">The price depends on the size, number of people, and painting techniques. The\r\nmore people are on a picture, the more difficult it is to accomplish.</p>\r\nTo get more information about the price, visit our page.'),
(4538, 371, '_faq_2_items_0_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4539, 371, 'faq_2_items_1_title', 'When do I pay for my portrait?'),
(4540, 371, '_faq_2_items_1_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4541, 371, 'faq_2_items_1_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">Only 10% at the beginning and 90% at the end when the last review is approved by\r\nyou.</p>'),
(4542, 371, '_faq_2_items_1_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4543, 371, 'faq_2_items_2_title', 'Can I pay in installments?'),
(4544, 371, '_faq_2_items_2_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4545, 371, 'faq_2_items_2_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">Yes, sure. With PayPal Credit up to 6 months.</p>'),
(4546, 371, '_faq_2_items_2_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4547, 371, 'faq_2_items', '3'),
(4548, 371, '_faq_2_items', 'field_5fb4d0a982848'),
(4549, 371, 'faq_3_title', 'Shipping'),
(4550, 371, '_faq_3_title', 'field_5fb4d0a482847'),
(4551, 371, 'faq_3_items_0_title', 'How long does it take to get the finished portrait?'),
(4552, 371, '_faq_3_items_0_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4553, 371, 'faq_3_items_0_text', '<ul class=\"faq__description-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ It depends on the size and the chosen technique.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ We guarantee that you will get your painting within the timelines or\r\neven the day earlier.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ Look here to see how long the whole process lasts.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ We are the fastest on the market.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4554, 371, '_faq_3_items_0_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4555, 371, 'faq_3_items_1_title', 'Can I get the portrait faster than the indicated delivery date?'),
(4556, 371, '_faq_3_items_1_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4557, 371, 'faq_3_items_1_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">Of course. You have to contact us via live chat. But the price will be 15-20%\r\nhigher as our artists have to make a bigger effort to complete your order faster.</p>\r\n<p class=\"faq__description\">You can choose:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"faq__description-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ Express service</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"faq__description-item\">⦁ Super express service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"faq__description\">It will reduce the shipping time by a few days.</p>'),
(4558, 371, '_faq_3_items_1_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4559, 371, 'faq_3_items_2_title', 'Do the portraits arrive safely without any damages?'),
(4560, 371, '_faq_3_items_2_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4561, 371, 'faq_3_items_2_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">Yes, we have special robust tubes that protect inner content. For example, this kind of wrapping we use for rolled charcoal portraits (see photo).</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq__description-image\"><img class=\"faq__description-photo\" src=\"http://gemaiter.me/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo-2.png\" alt=\"Do the portraits arrive safely without any damages?\" /></div>'),
(4562, 371, '_faq_3_items_2_text', 'field_5fb4d0bd8284a'),
(4563, 371, 'faq_3_items_3_title', 'Which countries do you ship to and how much does it cost?'),
(4564, 371, '_faq_3_items_3_title', 'field_5fb4d0b482849'),
(4565, 371, 'faq_3_items_3_text', '<p class=\"faq__description\">We ship our products to all the countries for FREE. You don’t have to pay for the delivery service.</p>'),
